data.description: Have you been dreaming of having a home in a private setting with gorgeous mountain views? Wait no longer, here it is! This lovely brick ranch has many updates. The home features three bedrooms, living room, large den with Vogelzang wood stove, and one bath. Also has a nice covered patio in the back and is sitting on approximately 18 acres. The updates include the following in 2004 new metal roof. In 2011 heat pump, 3/4 inch thick hickory hardwood, granite countertops, new windows, and doors. In 2014 travertine pavers laid on the porch and walkway, new carport, and back patio. More updates in 2022, remodeled utility room, new Pex waterlines were installed, new waste lines, new plastic and sump pump, were installed in the crawlspace, and new travertine pavers laid on front porch and heavy duty Handrail were installed. Lots of Wildlife on property. Now just imagine having your private approximate 18 acres, for hiking, hunting, and 4 wheeling. All this and just 18 minutes away from Gate City. The property was Tested for Radon, radon in water, septic, and water in 2023 (all testing and inspections came back good).    Two parcel #71 A 41 and 71  A 45A Buyers to verify all information.
